      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;zeus&#34;&gt;Zeus&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zeus was born in (approximately) June 2016. He is a German Shepherd/Chihuahua mix (along with some other small dog breeds) and weighs around 34 pounds. He enjoys hiking, eating cheese, playing with squeaky toys, and taking naps.&lt;/p&gt;











